answer:
In your question when you state 'tifo vaccine', you may be referring to the inactivated typhoid vaccine. Please contact a travel health clinic near you to have them review your immunization records. The clinic can recommend any needed dose(s) of travel vaccines and costs.
Immunization Nurse
